cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use AxiomStack or DorkLLM, please cite the software as below."
title: "AxiomStack: proof, probability, and production for local language-model systems"
abstract: >-
  A local-first language-model systems lab combining DorkLLM, a compact
  decoder-only transformer implemented from scratch in PyTorch, with evaluation,
  retrieval, bounded agents, typed serving, and the DorkChat browser client.
  Educational-scale, statistically explicit, and engineered as one full-stack
  system.
type: software
